snippet.textDisplay: I came Rajasthan in 2002,I was 8-9 months old because of my father's transfer. I grew up in bhilwara (textile city of Rajasthan) I shifted to kota in 2017 for studies. I am 17 today. Almost poore 17 saal maine Rajasthan mei guzaare hain though I am from madhya Pradesh. When I left bhilwara and came kota ,mujhe hi pata hai kya feel hua tha uss waqt mujhe 😅I couldn't stop crying. Being in kota,I still have a touch of Rajasthan! And unfortunately,I have to leave Rajasthan for my further studies. I just want to say ye song sun ke bas rona aa jata hai mujhe, believe nahi hota bas 2-3 months baad mujhe Rajasthan se jaana hoga. I have tears :') jab bhi ye song sunti hu,poori 17 years ki life yaad aajati hai jo yahan guzari hai. Shukriya Rajasthan. Hamesha dil mei rahega ye state :')
